			<h3>The future of Apache</h3>
			<p>As Apache is maintained regularly, it appears to become a staple of web server technology and without reason of discontinuation as it is based on the layered protocols of TCP/IP which are utilised through the web, its usage is unlikely to ever drop off. The only threat to the use of Apache is its many competitors. 
